I wouldn't necessarily say there

33:01.247 --> 33:04.915
was a bad part of greenfield.

33:04.916 --> 33:08.419
I mean, it's probably pretty

33:08.420 --> 33:11.356
spread out, bad, I
guess you'd say.

33:11.357 --> 33:12.224
What would you do?

33:12.225 --> 33:13.258
Come here to shoot up?

33:13.259 --> 33:13.959
Yep.

33:13.960 --> 33:15.893
You know we'd go down here and

33:15.894 --> 33:16.927
