Basically you'd come down

33:23.902 --> 33:27.238
here, shoot up, and what
are you going to nod out?

33:27.239 --> 33:30.208
Just sit down... just
sit down and hang out.

33:30.209 --> 33:32.977
A day like this, hang out under

33:32.978 --> 33:34.212
the underpass over there.

33:34.213 --> 33:37.815
Not exactly la vida loca.

33:37.816 --> 33:39.650
As you can see the trash and

33:39.651 --> 33:41.586
yuck, it's dirty and gross.

33:41.587 --> 33:46.091
There's probably people
who live down here.

33:46.092 --> 33:46.792
Really?

33:46.793 --> 33:52.397
Yeah, there's a lot of
homeless people in greenfield.

33:52.398 --> 33:53.898
What do you think now when

33:53.899 --> 33:56.401
you see somebody who's
junk sick on the street?

33:56.402 --> 33:58.836
It gives me that
yuck, sick feeling.

33:58.837 --> 33:59.937
And it scares me.

33:59.938 --> 34:02.973
It reminds me why I don't
want to be out there.

34:02.974 --> 34:03.909
It's just scary.

34:03.910 --> 34:08.779
A friend of mine overdosed
January 1st of this year.

34:08.780 --> 34:10.148
And my brother-in-law overdosed

34:10.149 --> 34:12.449
in Wendy's bathroom
