34:12.451 --> 34:14.152
And they brought
him back to life.

34:14.152 --> 34:15.253
He was dead in the bathroom.

34:15.254 --> 34:19.257
Uh-huh.

34:19.257 --> 34:22.659
So this is my narc cam.

34:22.661 --> 34:24.161
I carry this around, I have one

34:24.163 --> 34:28.299
of these in my house and
