34:28.300 --> 34:29.800
I have a fear that my husband's

34:29.801 --> 34:32.270
going to relapse and I'm
going to find him dead.

34:32.271 --> 34:35.806
You just put this in here and
squirt it up their nose.

34:35.806 --> 34:37.475
Now in most cases, as I

34:37.476 --> 34:39.310
understand it, they're
right out of it.

34:39.311 --> 34:44.681
They're right out of
it and instantly sick.

34:44.683 --> 34:45.284
They don't wake up happy.

34:45.284 --> 34:46.152
But they wake up.

34:46.152 --> 34:47.217
Somebody's blue there.

34:47.219 --> 34:47.985
On the floor.

34:47.987 --> 34:49.454
Are you saving that life?

34:49.455 --> 34:51.289
Yep, saving that life.

34:51.290 --> 34:51.590
Absolutely.

