My kids have been
home three years.

35:03.569 --> 35:05.903
You know, I no longer
have to watch my back.

35:05.904 --> 35:11.242
You know, I live a pretty
straight and narrow life.

35:11.243 --> 35:12.243
Which, you know, people might

35:12.244 --> 35:14.479
say is boring, but I
love my life today.

35:14.480 --> 35:15.314
I'm grateful.

