Given the opioid heroin

35:42.241 --> 35:43.408
addiction in our community, we'd

35:43.409 --> 35:45.743
like to start the conversation.

35:45.744 --> 35:46.877
What happened at that point of

35:46.878 --> 35:48.112
our life, what that was like.

