36:17.243 --> 36:20.077
What are the odds you're
going to own a house?

36:20.078 --> 36:21.879
What's the odds to
have a nice car?

36:21.880 --> 36:22.414
Any car?

36:22.415 --> 36:25.082
A place to live, all that stuff?

36:25.083 --> 36:29.554
Seems less and less
