I'll tell you something
really shameful about myself.

36:58.083 --> 37:03.621
The first time I shot up I
looked at myself with a big

37:03.622 --> 37:03.922
grin.

37:03.923 --> 37:08.092
Something was missing in me
whether it was a self-image

37:08.093 --> 37:11.362
situation, whether it was a

37:11.363 --> 37:14.198
character flaw, stable family,

37:14.199 --> 37:16.467
the suburbs, I had a lot of

37:16.468 --> 37:19.136
advantages, there was some dark

37:19.137 --> 37:21.205
genie inside me that I hesitate

37:21.206 --> 37:23.308
to call a disease that led me to

37:23.309 --> 37:25.610
dope, you know, I didn't have

37:25.611 --> 37:29.647
