37:37.656 --> 37:39.857
I never would have thought... I

37:39.858 --> 37:42.660
looked in a mirror and I saw

37:42.661 --> 37:45.363
somebody worth saving or that I

37:45.364 --> 37:47.998
wanted to at least try
real hard and save.

37:47.999 --> 37:53.504
You know, anybody can find
