37:59.578 --> 38:02.079
You know, that was daddy.

38:02.080 --> 38:03.714
Ain't no doubt about it but I

38:03.715 --> 38:06.517
hope I'll be able to say
that was daddy then.

38:06.518 --> 38:09.887
This is daddy now that I'm
